,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-03T08:25:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>98分鐘有啲誇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我身型偏肥都係六十鬆啲就跑完10k<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但我平常有做開運動</blockquote><br />\n樓主平時零運動<br />\n無得比嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"be6d707f13e775129b0b47685be299a95d89de3e","tid":385423,"uid":67976,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-03T08:26:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />98分鐘你不如唔好跑啦<br />\n我個女仔fd都係用78分鐘跑完 平時佢都唔係成日跑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fc6f69bb73348ddec68e0e85f13746c76020ede1","tid":385423,"uid":123335,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-03T08:26:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>98分鐘有啲誇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我身型偏肥都係六十鬆啲就跑完10k<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但我平常有做開運動</blockquote><br />\n我平時完全冇練跑 <br />\n最多係打下table tennis <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dd91f01c6f2c0ee8c9939d8c77c914d535247256","tid":385423,"uid":34572,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-03T08:26:40.000Z","msg":"有練開嘅預一個鐘"},{"pid":"b81d79711053a0fedc512e19b84251806235ab7c","tid":385423,"uid":72687,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-03T08:27:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>玩命</blockquote><br />\n渣打1月先跑<br />\n想家陣開始練<br />\n但唔知正常男人大概買幾耐 <br />\n有冇巴打知？</blockquote><br />\n正常應該1個鐘左右</blockquote><br />\n意思係指有練開，會跑到60分鐘左右 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n60分鐘應該係冇練開, 但身體正常<br />\n練開就50分鐘, 專業級就40分鐘<br />\n70分鐘叫弱, 80分鐘叫好弱,<br />\n90分鐘叫極弱<br />\nbtw, 如果你跑揸馬10K<br />\n90分鐘先跑完係冇證書的<br />\n<br />\n你應該由練5K開始,<br />\n直到可以40分鐘跑到5K先<br />\n之後再練40分鐘跑6K<br />\n再練50分鐘跑7K<br />\n再練60分鐘跑8K<br />\n再練60分鐘跑9K<br />\n再練60分鐘跑10K<br />\n<br />\n60分鐘內跑唔到10K<br />\n參加完你都唔好意思post出黎呃like<br />\n只會俾人笑尻你<br />\n<br />\n申利: 21K半馬, 2小時內"},{"pid":"716aa14b19fdd404735b281a8c59f1e4db0009a9","tid":385423,"uid":10338,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-03T08:27:50.000Z","msg":"有練開真係60分鐘左近"},{"pid":"b624dae0104e5ac21f9596d60b19ce3ee3d4c38e","tid":385423,"uid":56219,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-03T08:30:17.000Z","msg":"我48分左右"},{"pid":"5fe5ef691709c5068e329f93d9b214f99b3404bd","tid":385423,"uid":55445,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-03T08:30:42.000Z","msg":"50MINS 內啦"},{"pid":"a338d003ac448b9cec826b0868d87a259c8c1385","tid":385423,"uid":101231,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-03T08:31:04.000Z","msg":"我180 68kg男 有做開運動 第一次10k冇準備跑60分鐘 <br />\n<br />\n另外聽過人講渣馬10k平均係71分鐘<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n加油<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/38.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5670936a146f81b0aa19b0cd25f5e85b94fa6d8e","tid":385423,"uid":55445,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-03T08:31:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>50MINS 內啦</blockquote><br />\n183CM <br />\n練左一個月 上年跑48MINS <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"33da27e59a5fb57c9b1bb621df2563d91e5ec465","tid":385423,"uid":39853,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-03T08:33:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>我參加左三年，第一年7x分鐘，第二年53分鐘 ，上年44分鐘，<span style=\"color: red;\">其實練習多啲</span>，等自己習慣就得</blockquote><br />\n1個星期抽到兩日黎練<br />\n巴打覺得夠唔夠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n個個唔同，我冇特別去訓練長跑，不過一星期有兩三日去踢下波咁"},{"pid":"c4246d9ac8c4c98a5343012bbf25aac617472b54","tid":385423,"uid":22309,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-03T08:35:49.000Z","msg":"女仔跑都係70分鐘到<br />\nBtw跑90好似要上車唔洗跑<img src=\